$default_templates["templates"][] = array(
	"name"			=> esc_html__( "Page With Gradient Text", "sobari" ),
	"weight"		=> 0,
	"content"		=> '[vc_row css_animation="fadeIn" css=".vc_custom_1511318119682{padding-top: 8% !important;padding-bottom: 8% !important;}"][vc_column][gradient_text heading_tag="h1" text_color_1="#2ba7ef" text_color_2="#ff7cbd" gradient_direction="diagonal" text_content="Attention to detail is of most importance when you want to look good."][vc_empty_space height="40px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Delete the negative; accentuate the positive! My shows are about the complete woman who swallows it all. Its a question of survival. I didnt consider myself a fashion designer at all at the time of punk. I was just using fashion as a way to express my resistance and to be rebellious.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]I came from the country, and by the time I got to London, I considered myself to be very stupid. It was my ambition to understand the world I live in. I am what I am. Before I was not so proud to make fashion. My family thought fashion wasnt very interesting. So I hid that. I want people to be afraid of the women I dress.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]',
